commit.message: refs #194 Added check to score a 'merge branch' commit to 0.
Altered ENC_KEY length in travis yml

Fixed bug: Wrong round assigned to activity and commits

refs #141. Added a callback in Activity and Commit models to assign
Round as per commented_on and commit date respectively.
Added support to display activity description as parsed markdown

Updated the Activity Schema to accomodate event_action

1) Added event_action to the Activity model.
2) Allowed only opened and reopened issues for scoring.
Removed cosmetic changes from Home controller
Fixed controller method scopes. Removed unwanted routes
Added test cases for Admin::DashboardController and ReposHelper

Added some model and controller tests

Added test for :
Models: Commit, Score
Controllers: Goals, Home, Judging, Organizations, Transactions, Widgets
Altered gems with github paths to use https protocol to fix 'bundle' warnings.
Updated seeds.rb & home_helper to ease setup in dev env
